projects.name: Rent-Ease
projects.description: Rental house project utilizes a robust tech stack comprising React JS, Node JS, and MySQL to offer a seamless and efficient rental management solution. At its core, the system employs React JS for dynamic user interfaces, ensuring an intuitive and responsive experience for both landlords and tenants and enhance the user efficiency.

projects.name: Medi-Book
projects.description: Doctor Appointment System is a web application designed to streamline the process of scheduling appointments with healthcare professionals in efficient way. Built using ReactJS for the frontend, NodeJS for the backend, and MySQL for the database, this system offers users an intuitive interface to book appointments, manage their schedules, and receive reminders.

projects.name: Tour Management
projects.description: This application simplifies tour organization and booking. Using Html,Css,JavaScript for the frontend and NodeJS with MySQL for the backend, it enables seamless browsing of tour packages, easy booking, and secure payments. Admins can manage tours, while customers can leave reviews. With a user-friendly interface and secure technology stack, it enhances the tour experience for both operators and travelers.
